[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7335,
        "end_time": 9329,
        "text": "It&#39;s only been the last few hundreds years or so"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 9329,
        "end_time": 12088,
        "text": "that Western civilization has been putting art in museums,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12088,
        "end_time": 13803,
        "text": "at least museums resembling"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 13803,
        "end_time": 17231,
        "text": "the public institutions we know today."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17231,
        "end_time": 21049,
        "text": "Before this, for most, art served other purposes."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 21049,
        "end_time": 23094,
        "text": "What we call fine art today"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23094,
        "end_time": 25430,
        "text": "was, in fact, primarily how people experienced"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 25430,
        "end_time": 28223,
        "text": "an aesthetic dimension of religion."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 28223,
        "end_time": 31810,
        "text": "Paintings, sculpture, textiles and illuminations"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 31810,
        "end_time": 33720,
        "text": "were the media of their time,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 33720,
        "end_time": 35357,
        "text": "supplying vivid imagery"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 35357,
        "end_time": 39293,
        "text": "to accompany the stories of the day."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 39293,
        "end_time": 41116,
        "text": "In this sense, Western art"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 41116,
        "end_time": 42862,
        "text": "shared a utilitarian purpose"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 42862,
        "end_time": 44612,
        "text": "with other cultures around the world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 44612,
        "end_time": 50048,
        "text": "some of whose languages incidentally have no word for art."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 50048,
        "end_time": 53379,
        "text": "So how do we define what we call art?"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 53379,
        "end_time": 55167,
        "text": "Generally speaking, what we&#39;re talking about here"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 55167,
        "end_time": 57112,
        "text": "is work that visually communicates"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 57112,
        "end_time": 58753,
        "text": "meaning beyond language,"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 58753,
        "end_time": 60466,
        "text": "either through representation"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 60466,
        "end_time": 63769,
        "text": "or the arrangement of visual elements in space."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 63769,
        "end_time": 66179,
        "text": "Evidence of this power of iconography,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 66179,
        "end_time": 68613,
        "text": "or ability of images to convey meaning,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 68613,
        "end_time": 70391,
        "text": "can be found in abundance"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 70391,
        "end_time": 71727,
        "text": "if we look at art from"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 71727,
        "end_time": 74279,
        "text": "the histories of our major world religions."
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 74279,
        "end_time": 76814,
        "text": "Almost all have, at one time or another in their history,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 76814,
        "end_time": 79817,
        "text": "gone through some sort of aniconic phase."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 79817,
        "end_time": 84584,
        "text": "Aniconism prohibits any visual depiction of the divine."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 84584,
        "end_time": 86991,
        "text": "This is done in order to avoid idolatry,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 86991,
        "end_time": 91413,
        "text": "or confusion between the representation of divinity and divinity itself."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 91413,
        "end_time": 93029,
        "text": "Keeping it real, so to speak,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 93029,
        "end_time": 96917,
        "text": "in the relationship between the individual and the divine."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 96917,
        "end_time": 98946,
        "text": "However, this can be a challenge to maintain,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 98946,
        "end_time": 101379,
        "text": "given that the urge to visually represent and interpret"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 101379,
        "end_time": 102861,
        "text": "the world around us"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 102861,
        "end_time": 105768,
        "text": "is a compulsion difficult to suppress."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 105768,
        "end_time": 107802,
        "text": "For example, even today,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 107802,
        "end_time": 110888,
        "text": "where the depiction of Allah or the Prophet Muhammad is prohibited,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 110888,
        "end_time": 113268,
        "text": "an abstract celebration of the divine"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 113268,
        "end_time": 117692,
        "text": "can still be found in arabesque patterns of Islamic textile design,"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 117692,
        "end_time": 119563,
        "text": "with masterful flourishes of brushwork"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 119563,
        "end_time": 120843,
        "text": "and Arabic calligraphy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 120843,
        "end_time": 122107,
        "text": "where the words of the prophet"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 122107,
        "end_time": 125570,
        "text": "assume a dual role as both literature and visual art."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 125570,
        "end_time": 128114,
        "text": "Likewise, in art from the early periods"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 128114,
        "end_time": 130300,
        "text": "of Christianity and Buddhism,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 130300,
        "end_time": 132245,
        "text": "the divine presence of the Christ and the Buddha"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 132245,
        "end_time": 133913,
        "text": "do not appear in human form"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 133913,
        "end_time": 136113,
        "text": "but are represented by symbols."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 136113,
        "end_time": 137165,
        "text": "In each case,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 137165,
        "end_time": 139112,
        "text": "iconographic reference is employed"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 139112,
        "end_time": 140977,
        "text": "as a form of reverence."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 140977,
        "end_time": 143088,
        "text": "Anthropomorphic representation,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 143088,
        "end_time": 145090,
        "text": "or depiction in human form,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 145090,
        "end_time": 147647,
        "text": "eventually became widespread in these religions"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 147647,
        "end_time": 149263,
        "text": "only centuries later,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 149263,
        "end_time": 153638,
        "text": "under the influence of the cultural traditions surrounding them."
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 153638,
        "end_time": 154612,
        "text": "Historically speaking,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 154612,
        "end_time": 156645,
        "text": "the public appreciation of visual art"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 156645,
        "end_time": 159730,
        "text": "in terms other than traditional, religious or social function"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 159730,
        "end_time": 161564,
        "text": "is a relatively new concept."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 161564,
        "end_time": 165110,
        "text": "Today, we fetishize the fetish, so to speak."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 165110,
        "end_time": 167197,
        "text": "We go to museums to see art from the ages,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 167197,
        "end_time": 168862,
        "text": "but our experience of it there"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 168862,
        "end_time": 170529,
        "text": "is drastically removed from the context"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 170529,
        "end_time": 173361,
        "text": "in which it was originally intended to be seen."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 173361,
        "end_time": 175446,
        "text": "It might be said that the modern viewer"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 175446,
        "end_time": 177162,
        "text": "lacks the richness of engagement"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 177162,
        "end_time": 178918,
        "text": "that she has with contemporary art,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 178918,
        "end_time": 181060,
        "text": "which has been created relevant to her time"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 181060,
        "end_time": 183780,
        "text": "and speaks her cultural language."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 183780,
        "end_time": 186091,
        "text": "It might also be said that the history of what we call art"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 186091,
        "end_time": 188634,
        "text": "is a conversation that continues on,"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 188634,
        "end_time": 190947,
        "text": "as our contemporary present passes into what will be"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 190947,
        "end_time": 194196,
        "text": "some future generation&#39;s classical past."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 194196,
        "end_time": 195807,
        "text": "It&#39;s a conversation that reflects"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 195807,
        "end_time": 200104,
        "text": "the ideologies, mythologies, belief systems and taboos"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 200104,
        "end_time": 203294,
        "text": "and so much more of the world in which it was made."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 203294,
        "end_time": 205715,
        "text": "But this is not to say that work from another age"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 205715,
        "end_time": 208488,
        "text": "made to serve a particular function in that time"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 208488,
        "end_time": 211779,
        "text": "is dead or has nothing to offer the modern viewer."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 211779,
        "end_time": 213612,
        "text": "Even though in a museum setting"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 213612,
        "end_time": 215779,
        "text": "works of art from different places and times"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 215779,
        "end_time": 217529,
        "text": "are presented alongside each other,"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 217529,
        "end_time": 219447,
        "text": "isolated from their original settings,"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 219447,
        "end_time": 221749,
        "text": "their juxtaposition has benefits."
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 221749,
        "end_time": 224624,
        "text": "Exhibits are organized by curators,"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 224624,
        "end_time": 225861,
        "text": "or people who&#39;ve made a career"
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 225861,
        "end_time": 228696,
        "text": "out of their ability to recontextualize or remix"
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 228696,
        "end_time": 232676,
        "text": "cultural artifacts in a collective presentation."
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 232676,
        "end_time": 235472,
        "text": "As viewers, we&#39;re then able to consider the art"
    },
    {
        "index": 94,
        "start_time": 235472,
        "end_time": 237774,
        "text": "in terms of a common theme that might not be apparent"
    },
    {
        "index": 95,
        "start_time": 237774,
        "end_time": 239298,
        "text": "in a particular work"
    },
    {
        "index": 96,
        "start_time": 239298,
        "end_time": 241529,
        "text": "until you see it alongside another,"
    },
    {
        "index": 97,
        "start_time": 241529,
        "end_time": 246024,
        "text": "and new meanings can be derived and reflected upon."
    },
    {
        "index": 98,
        "start_time": 246024,
        "end_time": 247234,
        "text": "If we&#39;re so inclined,"
    },
    {
        "index": 99,
        "start_time": 247234,
        "end_time": 249196,
        "text": "we might even start to see every work of art"
    },
    {
        "index": 100,
        "start_time": 249196,
        "end_time": 252768,
        "text": "as a complementary part of some undefined, unified whole"
    },
    {
        "index": 101,
        "start_time": 252768,
        "end_time": 254742,
        "text": "of past human experience,"
    },
    {
        "index": 102,
        "start_time": 254742,
        "end_time": 257159,
        "text": "a trail that leads right to our doorstep"
    },
    {
        "index": 103,
        "start_time": 257159,
        "end_time": 259270,
        "text": "and continues on with us,"
    },
    {
        "index": 104,
        "start_time": 259270,
        "end_time": 262582,
        "text": "open to anyone who wants to explore it."
    }
]